<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Library/Struggle/bosnia_letter.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040942 text/html 5780
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:09:46 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
