<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Poetry/this_afternoon.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040040 text/html 681
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:00:45 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 511
Last-modified: Sun, 24 Nov 1996 06:09:22 GMT
