<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>This Afternoon</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR = "FFFFFF" TEXT = "000000">
<H2><CENTER>This Afternoon</CENTER></H2>

In spite of all
<BR>which lives and loves,
<BR>and dies and moves,
<BR>does, undoes.
<P>
Before i leave my room
<BR>this afternoon
<BR>I turn, and stooping
<BR>through the incense,
<BR>kiss this pillow dear
<BR>where our heads so recently were.
<P>
But know
<BR>that though only
<BR>five weeks,
<BR>a lifetime
<BR>has passed through.
<P>
and I will miss you.
</BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
