<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Beautiful Moon (Ballad of Dave and Judy)</TITLE></HEAD><BODY> 
<H2><CENTER>Beautiful Moon (Ballad of Dave and Judy)</CENTER></H2>

I don't want to fight anymore<BR>
let's fuck<BR>
fuck, fuck, fuck<BR>
let's go blind beneath their feet<BR>
fuck, fuck, fuck<BR>
let's fuck<BR>
I'm tired of your sarcasm<BR>
you're tired of my guilt<BR>
let's fuck<BR>
fuck, fuck, fuck<BR>
I want you to talk to me<BR>
you want me to talk<BR>
but you walk alone<BR>
and I'm hard as a rock<BR>
so let's fuck<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
