    Chapter 325 excerpt, banning the use of Clipper technology in the 
    encryption of medial records. Authored by state Rep. Marc Asch. Passed 
    into law May 11, 1994.
<DT><a href="mykotronx.notes"><B>mykotronx.notes</B></a>
