Gilmore's S/WAN, IPSec and Domain Name System Security overview page</A></B>

 <DT><B><A HREF="http://www.rsa.com/rsa/SWAN/swandef.htm">S/WAN 
Presentation</A></B>
<DD>Web-based slide presentation on S/WAN (Secure Wide-Area Network), an 
 initiative
   to promote multi-vendor virtual private networks among firewall and
   TCP/IP vendors. The initiative will mae recommendations and additions to
   underlying IPSec standard to acheive this goal.
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.rsa.com/rsa/SWAN/">RSA Data Security's S/WAN 
Archive</A></B>
