Engineering Task Force IPSec Working Group</A></B>
<DT><B><A 
HREF="http://playground.sun.com/pub/ipng/html/ipng-main.html">Info on 
Internet Protocol Version 6</A> (IPv6)</B>
<DD>Includes standards for privacy/security over the Internet, via 
encryption.
</DL>

