<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Legal Cases - FOIA/Privacy - Gilmore/Tien/EPIC Clipper Cases&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD><BODY>

