<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Hollywood Lick</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Hollywood Lick</CENTER></H2>

Smiling faces fade into the sunset as they<BR>
crawl <BR>
from the depths of<BR>
the city.<BR>
Careful<BR>
glances shroud<BR>
subconscious terror<BR>
I love you<BR>
<P>
I'll go out though none of you see me<BR>
you're too wasted or too dumb<BR>
tonight I'll taste the blood of the hunt<BR>
and start awake for years <BR>
to come<BR>
<P>
Sugar babe and sugar daddy<BR>
don't think they see me as I walk into the alley<BR>
come with me and you and<BR>
I are gonna find a place<BR>
where they'll never find<BR>
your body<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
