<DT><B><a href="http://thomas.loc.gov/">Thomas</a></B>
<DD>The Library of Congress Legislation & Federal Register Search Service.
Hot stuff!  <I>WARNING: Users of the EFF legislation archives should check
for updates from Thomas frequently.  We get most of our bill texts from
Thomas, of course, so our copies of bills are second-hand. We tell you
which ones have civil liberties and networking implications, Thomas tells
you what they look like and where they stand this week.</I>
