<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Censorship &amp; Privacy - Terrorism Hysteria &amp; Militia Fingerpointing&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Censorship/Terrorism_militias/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Nov 06 11:19:01 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<br>
   Note: Terrorism and militias are grouped together here because the
   tactics and rhetoric for instituting censorship and surveillance using
   &quot;terrorism&quot; and &quot;militias&quot; as excuses are similar. EFF neither implies 
   nor refutes any link or lack thereof between militia activities and 
   terrorism, and has no position on either, except as they relate to
   censorship.
<p>
