<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Prose/Complexity_threshold/ 204.253.162.4 19970108040432 text/html 4638
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:04:36 GMT
