<DT><a href="CPSR_v_FBI/"><B>CPSR_v_FBI/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory with information regarding CPSR's FOIA suit 
    against the FBI
<DT><a href="CPSR_v_NSA/"><B>CPSR_v_NSA/</B></A>
<DD>Directory with information regarding CPSR's attack on the
    NSA and its clipper policy
<DT><a href="Clipper_FOIA/"><B>Clipper_FOIA/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory of files from Clipper-related FOIA cases,
    incl. Gilmore &amp; Tien v. NSA.
<DT><a href="EPIC_v_FBI/"><B>EPIC_v_FBI/</B></A>
<DD>Directory containing information regarding EPIC's lawsuit 
    the FBI
<DT><a href="Foreign_and_local/"><B>Foreign_and_local/</B></A>
<DD>directory containing documents related to FOIA from
    elsewhere
<DT><a href="Gilmore_v_NSA/"><B>Gilmore_v_NSA/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory documents pertaining to Gilmore's various 
    FOIA suits against the NSA
<DT><a href="ITAR_FOIA/"><B>ITAR_FOIA/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory of documents about ITAR export 
    restrictions on cryptographic products, obtained via FOIA request.
</DL>

