<P></CENTER><BR><HR>
<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="wa_h1111_95.bill"><B>wa_h1111_95.bill</B></a>
<DD>the WA state telecom reform bill, House version
    (Senate version is wa_sb5156_95.bill). Vetoed by the governor as
    hindering, not helping, progress and competitiveness.
<DT><a href="wa_h1111_sb5156_95.history"><B>wa_h1111_sb5156_95.history</B></a>
<DD>(a.k.a. wa_sb5156_h1111_95.history) legislative
    history of SB5156 and H1111
<DT><a href="wa_h1111_sb5156_95_lowry.veto"><B>wa_h1111_sb5156_95_lowry.veto</B></a>
<DD>WA Gov. Lowry's veto statement regarding
    his killing of bill SB5156. 
<DT><a href="wa_sb5156_95.bill"><B>wa_sb5156_95.bill</B></a>
<DD>the WA state telecom reform bill, Senate version 
    (House version is wa_h1111_95.bill). Vetoed by the governor as 
    hindering, not helping, progress and competitiveness.
</DL>

<br><hr><br>
