<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Privacy - Caller ID - Ohio&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD><BODY>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<H1><TD><A HREF="http://www.eff.org/">EFFWeb Welcome Page</A></TD></H1>
