<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF "Cyborg Anthropology" Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD><BODY>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="/">EFFWeb Welcome Page</A></TD><H1></H1>
