    <dd>Essays in Postmodern Culture . Introduction: Antinomy in the Net. 
    George Yudice, "Feeding the Transcendent Body" . Alison Fraiberg, 
    "Of AIDS, Cyborgs, and Other Indiscretions" . David Porush and 
    Alison Fraiberg, Commentary on "Of AIDS, ...
