<DT><a href="Anonymity/"><B>Anonymity/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory about more general online 
    anonymity/pseudonymity issues.
<DT><a href="Crypto_misc/"><B>Crypto_misc/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory of info on general (usually technical)
    encryption topics.
<DT><a href="Digital_signature/"><B>Digital_signature/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory of info regarding the related 
    technology of digital signature and electronic authentication.
</DL>

