<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/bang_sign2_icon.gif">
EFF "Legal Cases - Church of Scientology" Archive</h1>

<h5>
<br>ftp.eff.org, /pub/Legal/Cases/Scientology_cases/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Legal/Cases/Scientology_cases
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/Scientology_cases/
</h5>
<BR>

Disclaimer: EFF has NO POSITION of any kind on whether or not the
Church of Scientology "is" or "isn't" a religion, or any other such issues.
We are interested solely in, and are achiving documents related to only,
CoS's actions and legal cases as they intersect with issues of online free
speech, publication and association.<P>



