<h2><A NAME="files"></a>
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" 
ALT=""></A> Files in this Archive (listed by date)</h2>

<DL>
<DT><A HREF="HTML/about_cos_docs.html">Information about this archive and 
these documents.</A>

<DT><A HREF="9thcir_080294_seal.remand"><B>9thcir_080294_seal.remand</B></A>
<DD>The 9th Circuit Court of Appeals decision
   remanding back to the district court the question of the relevance of CoS
   docs in the Fishman declaration, and the question of whether or not
   they should be sealed.  These are the documents at issue in the cases
   against Lerma and the Washington Post defendants.

<DT><A href="kobrin_inet-world.letter"><B>kobrin_inet-world.letter</B></A> 
   <DD>Letter of CoS attorney Helena Kobrin to _Internet_World_ in response to
   the magazine's questions about CoS's attempt to destroy the
   alt.religion.scientology Usenet newsgroup. Includes commentary on and
   criticism of the letter.
<DT><A href="holzinger.article"><B>holzinger.article</B></A> 
   <DD>Article by Lee Holzinger about the case (very sympathetic to CoS 
   viewpoint) 
<DT><A href="erlich_experience.article"><B>erlich_experience.article</B></A> 
   <DD>Article by Erlich detailing the search of his house by CoS agents
<DT><A href="eff_cos_012395.letter"><B>eff_cos_012395.letter</B></A> 
   <DD>Open letter from EFF to CoS
<DT><A href="a-b_020895.exhibits"><B>a-b_020895.exhibits</B></A> 
   <DD>Exhibits A and B in the Erlich case.
<DT><A href="cos_020895.complaint"><B>cos_020895.complaint</B></A> 
    <DD>Original complaint file by CoS against Erlich, Klemesrud & Netcom.
<DT><A href="cos_tro_020895.application"><B>cos_tro_020895.application</B></A> 
   <DD>CoS application for temporary restraining order against Erlich, 
Klemesrud & Netcom.
<DT><A href="erlich_tro_021095.order"><B>erlich_tro_021095.order</B></A> 
   <DD>Order for Temporary Restraining Order against Erlich, Klemesrud & 
Netcom.
