<h2><A NAME="offsite"></a>
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/earth2_icon.gif" 
ALT=""></A> Links to Related Off-Site Resources</h2>
DISCLAIMER: EFF has no position on most pro/con-CoS arguments whatsoever,
and presence of a link in this section does not indicate agreement of EFF
with the views espoused on such pages.  These links are provided for 
informational purposes. 

<DL>
<DT>Ron Newman's <a href="http://www.cybercom.net/~rnewman/scientology/home.html">Church of
 Scientology criticism</a> Archive
<DT>David Elrod's <A HREF="http://www.theta.com/">Church of Scientology</A>
Archive</A>
<DD>(appears to be an "official" CoS site.)
<DT>Karel Jeelof's <A HREF="http://www.digiface.nl/~kjeelof">Church of 
Scientology of Amsterdam</A> pages
<DD>(in Dutch; appears to be an "official" CoS site.)
<DT><A HREF="http://www.faegre.com/"><B>Faegre &amp; Benson</B></A>
<DD>(attorneys for FACTNet, in RTC [CoS] v. FACTNet.)
<DT><A HREF="http://gopher.well.com:70/1/Publications/online_zines/scam/">
<B>Scamizdat</B></A>
<DD>A large archive of articles and testimonials about CoS
<DT><A HREF="http://www.well.com/user/jerod23/clam.html"><B>Jerod Pore's 
Scientology Criticism Page</B></A> 
<DT><A HREF="http://mail.bris.ac.uk/%7Eplmlp/scum.html"><B>UK Scientology 
Critics' Info Page</B></A> 
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Society_and_Culture/Religion/Scientology/">
Yahoo's index of Scientology-related WWW sites</A></B>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.cnn.com/US/scientology/">CNN Online US News
report on 11/29 Brinkema ruling</A>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.eexi.gr/~antbos/SCIENTOL.HTM">Article from the 
Greek press about Scientology's legal trouble and conflict with authorities
in Greece
<DD>(CoS raided; espionage charges, exploitation charges, drug charges; 
trial/investigation underway)
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.scientology.org">The official Scientology Home 
Page</A></B>
<DD>In English, Fran&ccedil;ais, Deutsch, Italiano &amp; Espa&ntilde;ol
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.dianetics.org">The official Dianetics Home 
Page</A></B> 
<DD>In English, Fran&ccedil;ais, Deutsch, Italiano &amp; Espa&ntilde;ol
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.lronhubbard.org">The official L. Ron Hubbard 
(Scientology founder) info pages</A></B>
