<DOCNO>WT10-B07-171</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA016-000165-B038-3</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/pub/Intellectual_property/Scientology_cases/HTML/about_cos_docs.html 204.253.162.4 19970105205833 text/html 3479
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 20:58:37 GMT
