<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="README.xlate"><B>README.xlate</B></a>
<DD>A quicky readme file, almost in the form of a man page. 
<DT><a href="ab.p"><B>ab.p</B></a>
<DD>prints AaBbCcDdEeFfGgHhIiJjKkLlMmNnOoPpQqRrSsTtUuVvWwXxYyZz0123456789
    A 'test run' for some sorting stuff. 
<DT><a href="amper.p"><B>amper.p</B></a>
<DD>Test stuffs for translating special chars
<DT><a href="buildind.sh"><B>buildind.sh</B></a>
<DD>An old version of makeind.sh. Don't use it. 
<DT><a href="cookie.tar"><B>cookie.tar</B></a>
<DD>a couple cgi scripts to demonstrate how cookies can be used. 
<DT><a href="dbind.p"><B>dbind.p</B></a>
<DD>A re-write of findnoind.p which dumps SQL for oracle, text
    for a searchable index, and does multitudes of consistancy
    checking for all the archives. 
<DT><a href="finddups"><B>finddups</B></a>
<DD>finds directories which have multiple 00-INDEX.xxx files. 
<DT><a href="findnoind.p"><B>findnoind.p</B></a>
<DD>perl script to find directories that don't have indexes, etc. 
<DT><a href="fixit.p"><B>fixit.p</B></a>
<DD>will re-write some stuff built with old versions of xlate. Can be
    tried on older 00-index.html's, but no guarantees. 
<DT><a href="gettitle.p"><B>gettitle.p</B></a>
<DD>grabs the 'title' line from 00-links.html files. 
    No longer used. 19960423 dhb. 
<DT><a href="how_to_index"><B>how_to_index</B></a>
<DD>a text file with instructions on which scripts to 
    use and the proceedures to follow for building indexes. 
<DT><a href="links.sh"><B>links.sh</B></a>
<DD>builds the root links.html file, using gettitle.pl
    no longer used. See links.p 19960423 dhb. 
<DT><a href="links.p"><B>links.p</B></a>
<DD>builds the root links.html file, incorporated gettitle.pl
    Runs _LOTS_ faster. 
<DT><a href="makeind.p"><B>makeind.p</B></a>
<DD>builds 00-index.txt in a directory which doesn't have one.
<DT><a href="makeind.sh"><B>makeind.sh</B></a>
<DD>builds 00-index.txt in a directory which doesn't have one.
    Is now been replace by makeind.p 
<DT><a href="menu2ind.p"><B>menu2ind.p</B></a>
<DD>perl script to build 00-index.txt files from .menu's. 
    Called by makeind.sh
<DT><a href="search.tar"><B>search.tar</B></a>
<DD>tar file containing the scripts for the CGI-bin search
    engine. Rely's on a 00-index.txt file listing all the files in
    the archive. 
<DT><a href="skel.p"><B>skel.p</B></a>
<DD>skeleton of perl script with command line stuffs. 
<DT><a href="spec.b.01"><B>spec.b.01</B></a>
<DD>A very rough, dated version of the &quot;spec&quot; for these scripts. 
<DT><a href="spec_19960911"><B>spec_19960911</B></a>
<DD>A stil very rough, newer version of the &quot;spec&quot; for
    these scripts. 
<DT><a href="spec_current"><B>spec_current</B></a>
<DD>Hopefully the current spec for this stuff. 
<DT><a href="sponsor.p"><B>sponsor.p</B></a>
<DD>a quicky perl script that places a line of HTML randomly 
    selected from a list of sponsors into the root index.html files. 
<DT><a href="stripper.p"><B>stripper.p</B></a>
<DD>removes http://www.eff.org's
<DT><a href="urls.p"><B>urls.p</B></a>
<DD>grabs the urls from an html file and checks them, etc. 
    Has more than a few bugs. 
<DT><a href="version.p"><B>version.p</B></a>
<DD>The version ID file. Used by other scripts. 
<DT><a href="version2.p"><B>version2.p</B></a>
<DD>The 'developement' version of version.p
<DT><a href="xlate.p"><B>xlate.p</B></a>
<DD>(the in production version) builds 00-links.html files
    from 00-INDEX text files. 
<DT><a href="xlate2.p"><B>xlate2.p</B></a>
<DD>The under construction version of xlate.p. Very dangerous to
    use. May have features and bug fixes that xlate.p lacks. 
</DL>

