<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Poetry/moonlight_sonata.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040155 text/html 5305
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:02:00 GMT
