<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Peru&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/serv/ftp/pub/Legislation/Foreign_and_local/Peru/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Thu Jun 13 13:37:39 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><H1></H1>
