<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Library/Struggle/yanomami_centena.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040859 text/html 6638
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:09:04 GMT
