<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - EFF, ACLU, et al. v. Dept. of Justice (ACLU v. Reno)&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/EFF_ACLU_v_DoJ/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Fri Dec 06 16:41:21 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
