<a name="top">EFF &quot;Rating, Filtering and Labelling of Online Content&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Net_info/Tools/Ratings_filters_labelling/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Dec 11 13:20:31 PDT 1996</h6><br>
