<DL>
<DT><A HREF=".."><B>Up to the Parent Directory</B><P></a>
<DT><a href="Comm_Decency_Act/"><B>Comm_Decency_Act/</B></A>
<DD>link to directory of info on the Exon bill 
    (Communications Decency Act), the Leahy/Klink bill, the Cox/Wyden bill 
    and other legislation related to Internet censorship (and it's 
    prevention) and to issues surrounding net filtration and ratings systems.
</DL>

