<DT><a href="cda_960201_eff.statement"><B>cda_960201_eff.statement</B></a>
<DD>Condsider this a wake-up call. Our elected 
    officials have spoken, and...our Constitutional rights in the new 
    medium...have been unsurped. Strong EFF statement against the 
    unconstitutional Communications Decency Act.
<DT><a href="cda_051995_s652_amend.draft"><B>cda_051995_s652_amend.draft</B></a>
<DD>Draft amendment to the Exon Communications 
    Decency Act
