Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="pharmanet_bccla.announce"><B>pharmanet_bccla.announce</B></a>
<DD>British Columbia Civil Liberties Assoc's March
    1994 press release outlining the Pharmanet system.
<DT><a href="pharmanet_bccla.speech"><B>pharmanet_bccla.speech</B></a>
<DD>John Westwood's March 1994 speech attacking the
    pharmanet proposal
<DT><a href="pharmanet_bccla_alert.old"><B>pharmanet_bccla_alert.old</B></a>
<DD>BCCLA'a March 1994 press release attacking the
    Pharmanet project
<DT><a href="pharmanet_ipc.release"><B>pharmanet_ipc.release</B></a>
<DD>David Flaherty (Information and Privacy
    Commissioner) on March 1994 calls for public
    consultation on Pharmanet.
<DT><a href="pharmanet_manning.article"><B>pharmanet_manning.article</B></a>
<DD>Kelly Manning's March 1994 summary of the fall
    of the Pharmanet project following David Flaherty's
    recognition of the series privacy problems with the
    program. 
</DL>

