<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_trans_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - FOIA/Privacy - Gilmore/Tien/EPIC Clipper Cases&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org, /pub/Privacy/Clipper/Clipper_FOIA/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Privacy/Clipper/Clipper_FOIA
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Clipper/Clipper_FOIA/
