<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="art_21_constitution_english.jp"><B>art_21_constitution_english.jp</B></a>
<DD>article 21 of the Consitution of Japan (the
    often-violated prohibition against the passages of laws that interfer 
    with citizens' free expression or privacy.)
<DT><a href="constitution_english.jp"><B>constitution_english.jp</B></a>
<DD>The full Constitution of Japan, in English
<DT><a href="constitution_euc.jp.gz"><B>constitution_euc.jp.gz</B></a>
<DD>The full Constitution of Japan, in Japanese (Kanji).
    This version uses EUC encoding, and is gzip-compressed.
<DT><a href="constitution_iso-2022-jp.jp.gz"><B>constitution_iso-2022-jp.jp.gz</B></a>
<DD>The full Constitution of Japan, in 
    Japanese (Kanji). This version uses ISO-2022 encoding, and is 
    gzip-compressed.
<DT><a href="constitution_sjis.jp.gz"><B>constitution_sjis.jp.gz</B></a>
<DD>The full Constitution of Japan, in Japanese 
    (Kanji). This version uses Shift-JIS (SJIS) encoding, and is 
    gzip-compressed.
</DL>

