<A NAME="CIyxFw.DFo@cs.uiuc.edu">
_The Hacker Crackdown_ on-line</a>
<pre>
Newsgroups: comp.org.eff.talk,misc.legal,alt.comp.acad-freedom.talk,alt.wired,alt.etext,alt.society.civil-liberty,uiuc.civil-liberty
From: kadie@cs.uiuc.edu (Carl M Kadie)
Subject:  _The Hacker Crackdown_ on-line
