    1994. House Bill HB1627, Sponsored by Del. Joan Pitkin. Bill died 
    in committee, Mar. 24, 1994, unfortunately, mainly due to lack of 
    citizen activism to show support, counteract negative commentary from 
    telco and cableco reps, and educate less clueful members of the committee.
