<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="ripem.faq"><B>ripem.faq</B></a>
<DD>November 1993 version of Marc VanHeyningen's FAQ regarding
    RIPEM, a public key mail encryption program.
<DT><a href="rsa-faq.ps.gz"><B>rsa-faq.ps.gz</B></a>
<DD>Frequently Asked Questions and answers about RSA encryption
    software. This is a gzip-compressed PostScript document.
<DT><a href="rsa_patents.list"><B>rsa_patents.list</B></a>
<DD>may 1993 list of patent numbers for PKP/RSA's patents
<DT><a href="rsaref.license"><B>rsaref.license</B></a>
<DD>March 1994 licensing agreement for RSAREF program
</DL>

